e suite of, you know, family office type services. We have in-house will and tax specialists. Question? 00:28:27.580 --> 00:28:30.709 [ADVISOR]: Yeah, what, what financial planning software do you guys use? 00:28:30.710 --> 00:28:31.790 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: So, Conquest. 00:28:32.210 --> 00:28:32.810 [ADVISOR]: Okay. 00:28:32.810 --> 00:28:36.669 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: So, conquest for financial plans, very comprehensive, 00:28:36.670 --> 00:28:39.590 [ADVISOR]: We use the same thing, there's something I've branded at one plan. 00:28:39.590 --> 00:28:43.369 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Of course, of course. And that's a recent change. 00:28:43.790 --> 00:28:46.600 [ADVISOR]: For the last two, three years? 00:28:46.600 --> 00:28:50.640 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Okay, yeah, yeah. And it was, like a Navi plan? Was it NAVI plan? 00:28:50.640 --> 00:28:51.300 [ADVISOR]: Yeah. 00:28:51.300 --> 00:28:59.380 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Okay, yeah, yeah. So, fairly familiar. I think the whole industry is moving to Conquest as, using the financial planning software. 00:28:59.380 --> 00:29:22.249 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: But again, you know, just kind of, you know, closing out this discussion in terms of really being able to focus and saying, hey, listen, you know, we have a platform for advisors in which now we've institutionalized, you know, certain tasks, right? Such as, you know, providing in-house, you know, will and tax specialists who do complete tax returns as well as fully executed wills. That's cool. As well as, yeah, power of attorneys for your clients. 00:29:22.250 --> 00:29:31.839 [ADVISOR]: high net worth people want to see the one-stop shop, and I was just asked yesterday, I was on a pilot call. [CURRENT_DEALER] is partnering with… 00:29:32.840 --> 00:29:35.319 [ADVISOR]: Oh, I can't even remember the name. 00:29:35.530 --> 00:29:48.070 [ADVISOR]: was one of these firms, and it's interesting. The industry's going this way, I'd like to see that [CURRENT_DEALER], for now, is on board with it as a pilot, but I need to k