[ADVISOR]: Sorry, I just had a quick question. I noticed that you guys have the app there, the Optimize app. Is that something for… that I can add to my CRM on the road sort of thing, or is that just exclusively for advisors? 00:20:03.600 --> 00:20:04.120 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: The optimal… 00:20:04.120 --> 00:20:05.680 [ADVISOR]: Advisors to our clients. 00:20:06.340 --> 00:20:17.860 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: So these are for the advisors. This is, just strictly for the advisors. We are working for an… working on an app for our clients, but in terms of taking us on the road with you, yeah, this would be more for that. 00:20:17.860 --> 00:20:18.410 [ADVISOR]: there. 00:20:20.430 --> 00:20:21.270 [ADVISOR]: Thank you. 00:20:21.270 --> 00:20:22.460 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: No problem, no problem. 00:20:23.760 --> 00:20:48.759 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so in terms of providing you access with our future-ready technologies, what that means is that we've literally scoured the market, put together the best of the best, and have made them all available to you through that one central sign-in location. So for our CRM, we're using HubSpot, one of the largest CRMs out there. We think it's much better than Salesforce from an overall client servicing, prospecting, and user experience perspective. For onboarding and servicing, we've put together a complete end-to-end DocuSign 00:20:48.760 --> 00:20:55.140 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: a great solution. You also have Conquest for financial planning, we also use Bloomberg for trading and research, and so on and so on. 00:20:55.200 --> 00:20:59.749 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And I know we've touched on this in some of the other meetings, but again, just a little bit of a refresher here. 00:21:01.310 --> 00:21:02.549 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so… 00:21:04.280 --> 00:21:24.150 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: While a typical retail dealer out there nickel and dimes their advisors for these kinds of technologies, the overarching goal here at Optimize is to put together a technology stack that's provided to you at no cost. And so, we'll put you and your team at the front end of the technology and AI curve, all while ensuring it brings significant and consistent value to your clients and practice. 00:21:24.150 --> 00:21:39.800 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: So, through all of these different systems, here's annual savings of [TECH_SAVINGS_AMOUNTS] combined. Again, really trying to deliver as much value as we can into our advisors so that they're able to grow their practice, and maintain that, those client relationships. 00:21:40.590 --> 00:21:45.129 [ADVISOR]: That's amazing. So there's no… no cost to operating here? 00:21:45.370 --> 00:21:46.580 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Absolutely zero. 00:21:47.080 --> 00:21:47.780 [ADVISOR]: Okay. 00:21:50.770 --> 00:21:51.759 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so… 00:21:52.840 --> 00:21:57.680 [ADVISOR]: I mean, that's much different than most other places, aside from a major retail bank. 00:21:57.930 --> 00:22:00.510 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: No, absolutely, yeah, no, and that's kind of… 00:22:00.570 --> 00:22:19.260 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: That is, like I said, the overarching goal here is we want to invest in our advisors, make sure that they can run their practice as efficiently and as easily as possible, because at the end of the day, the more that they can grow their practice, the more that they can drive value into their practice, it obviously benefits both sides. 00:22:20.940 --> 00:22:39.200 [ADVISOR]: Sorry, and I know that this is sort of not really what you're discussing now, but do you guys… do you guys have, group plans? Like, group employee plans? You know, sometimes people have matching RSPs, or… or, you know, some sort of benefits package that, that, you know. 00:22:39.380 --> 00:22:52.899 [ADVISOR]: But that you would, you would have that, you know, something from [CURRENT_DEALER] or something like that. I know that [CURRENT_DEALER] is where I am now, but, you know, is there… is there a benefits package that comes with it, that comes with the office? 00:22:53.100 --> 00:22:59.