rts, in that your team will have access to our well-curated live dashboards and reports, which are consistently synced and updated. Again, these are synced by the minute. 00:29:27.040 --> 00:29:39.209 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so whether you want to track the status of your ongoing servicing requests, new account submissions, initiated transfers, or you want to see all of your clients who are turning 71 for those rollovers into RIPS, 00:29:39.210 --> 00:29:46.860 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Or you want to look at all of your clients' RESP client beneficiary and grant information. Everything is available with only a few clicks. 00:29:47.360 --> 00:29:48.060 [ADVISOR]: Okay. 00:29:50.110 --> 00:30:07.480 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And then lastly, we built out a series of very high-end client servicing workflows, personalized interactions and ongoing outbound communications. And so, you'll never have to spend time creating and sending content, maintaining email distribution lists, or monitoring content schedules. 00:30:07.480 --> 00:30:12.359 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: All, our team will take care of all of that in terms of building out, 00:30:12.360 --> 00:30:21.370 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: very effective client, drip campaigns. And so, this way, your clients will receive impactful content on a regular basis, all branded with you and your team. 00:30:21.710 --> 00:30:31.749 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so, as a result of eliminating all of these non-core activities, we consistently find that the technology easily puts back anywhere between 50% to 70% back in the advisor's data. 00:30:32.910 --> 00:30:36.930 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so, with those time savers, any kind of question, any other questions that you may have? 00:30:37.250 --> 00:30:39.450 [ADVISOR]: Not at the moment, no. 00:30:39.450 --> 00:30:40.559 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Okay, no problem. 00:30:41.130 --> 00:30:54.849 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And then, the third core benefit that our technology platform brings to the table is that it really elevates that client experience by virtue of us consistently scanning the market to identify and roll out a really amazing suite of client-facing technologies. 00:30:54.850 --> 00:31:07.989 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so, case in point is our financial planning software, Conquest. This combines a phenomenal high-end client experience with a fully AI-powered planning module that instantly uncovers opportunities and strategies while saving you significant time in the process. 00:31:08.220 --> 00:31:28.469 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so, imagine you're preparing a financial plan for a client, and all of their data, whether it's their investment accounts, their market values, their ongoing PACs or SWIPs, all of it was consistently synced across the platform, and so, again, you don't have to spend unnecessary time inputting that information anywhere. Or, imagine a client wasn't on track to meet their retirement goals for any number of reasons. 00:31:28.970 --> 00:31:48.059 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Perhaps their current savings rate isn't enough, or their desired retirement lifestyle is a little bit beyond their reach, or they're not maxing out on the various planning strategies. Whatever the reason, our AI-powered planning module named SAM will go in and literally run endless series of simulations to arrive at the most optimal recommendation possible. 00:31:48.060 --> 00:32:04.950 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so it does this by balancing all of Canada's current tax laws and all of the available financial planning strategies in the market with the client's specific priorities, desired goals, and stated savings capacity to arrive at that best possible financial plan and recommendation for your client. 00:32:04.950 --> 00:32:12.250 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so, not only will this level of simulation and analysis bring a ton of value, but it'll obviously save you a ton of time in the process. 00:32:12.790 --> 00:32:14.019 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Does that make sense? 00:32:14.020 --> 00:32:14.920 [ADVISOR]: Makes sense. 00:32:15.070 --> 00:32:15.730 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Great. 00:32:17.060 --> 00:32:17.810 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Cool. 00:32:18.160 --> 00:32:24.399 [ADVISOR]: Can I ask you one more thing? Can you just remind me, once again, if we can do corporate planning on Conquest? 00:32:24.680 --> 00:32:25.870 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Corporate planning? 00:32:25.870 --> 00:32:30.150 [ADVISOR]: Corporate accounts, and, like, we can hold corporate accounts or no corporate accounts. 00:32:31.770 --> 00:32:37.850 [ADVISOR]: And does Conquest allow that… that split between, 00:32:38.250 --> 00:32:41.970 [ADVISOR]: Corporate accounts when, when, when doing financial plans. 00:32:41.970 --> 00:32:48.239 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Yeah, yeah, so they definitely can do financial plans for corporate accounts. The only thing we don't do is the tax returns for those corporate accounts. 00:32:48.240 --> 00:32:50.359 [ADVISOR]: Right, okay, it was his tax returns, thank you. 00:32:50.360 --> 00:32:53.959 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Yeah, but yeah, in terms of running financial plans for them, yes. 00:32:53.960 --> 00:32:55.059 [ADVISOR]: Okay, thank you. 00:32:55.060 --> 00:32:56.480 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: No problem, no problem. 00:32:57.040 --> 00:33:09.409 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And then lastly, not only are the financial plans, planning reports themselves very high-end and client-friendly, we also make it extremely easy for you and your team to track and stay up on top of all of your clients' financial goals. 00:33:09.410 --> 00:33:30.899 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so we do that by providing financial planning reports in your dashboard. This is where you'll easily monitor, at a high level, each one of your clients' goals and their desired retirement lifestyle. And so you'll get a quick snapshot of their projected estate surpluses or deficits, which is automatically synced with their investments, their investments' current market values and savings plans. 00:33:30.980 --> 00:33:48.060 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: regardless of whether you have a meeting with a client 6 months from now, or a client calls yo