tive retirement or exit from the business. 00:04:58.610 --> 00:05:13.000 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: We're not, I'll say this up front, we're not chasing books here. I look much more qualitatively at the types of advisors that, that we've grown the platform with. We're not trying to push volume through the door. 00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:28.319 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: We're fully independent. We're extremely intentional about who we speak with. We don't run a rookie program. We only engage with very experienced, tenured premium advisors, with proven history, track records. 00:05:28.320 --> 00:05:42.619 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Strong reputation in the industry, and most importantly, for us is really a client-first mindset, and that's really a non-negotiable piece for us. This is very, exploratory, it's a multi- 00:05:42.620 --> 00:05:59.410 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: stage process for us, so there's no pressure at all, no obligation, there's no expectations here on either side. If we felt some alignment today, we'd spend some more time together walking through various parts of the business in more detail, and 00:05:59.410 --> 00:06:04.259 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Ultimately, we'd consider extending an invitation to have you join us here. 00:06:04.260 --> 00:06:13.419 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: for a mutual due diligence session with our senior leadership team. Does that sound reasonable, at least as a basis for today's conversation? 00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:15.330 [ADVISOR_1]: Absolutely. Absolutely. 00:06:15.330 --> 00:06:18.129 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Good. Just before I jump in, 00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:35.900 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: just, the team's put together some notes for me, on your practice, so I have a sense here of the length of time in the industry. I can see why you'd be on our radar. The size of your book, I've got in the [BOOK_SIZE_RANGE]. 00:06:35.900 --> 00:06:41.160 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: But it's certainly a very long and tenured career at [BANK_OWNED_DEALER]. 00:06:41.280 --> 00:06:58.440 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: So, I thought, you know, bef