ust to give you an idea, your book size would sort of put you in the middle of the pack here. We're supporting now [ADVISORY_TEAM_COUNT] advisory teams across the country. We manage [AUM_AMOUNT]. It's custody at [CUSTODIAN]. 00:19:05.210 --> 00:19:14.159 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: and any bank groups that have come over, that's been the shift. Regardless of what their unique value proposition and strategy has been, they've had to 00:19:14.160 --> 00:19:18.189 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Be at the point where they're thinking of, in terms of succession. 00:19:18.210 --> 00:19:31.610 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Right? And, yeah, I, you know, exactly. I can see that clearly. And then monetizing, you know, monetizing. And that's, you know, from our perspective, we pay, 00:19:31.720 --> 00:19:34.190 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: A 2% transition bonus. 00:19:34.230 --> 00:19:42.510 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Right? So, all the assets that move into our models, they said 2%, paid there over 36 months. 00:19:42.510 --> 00:19:58.040 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: We have a full 1% trailer, so there's no compression, no tech fees, marketing fees, desk fees, it's a full 1% trailer. And then on the exit, we pay 5% of AUM over 36 months. 00:19:58.050 --> 00:20:02.989 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: So I think you can see from, like, in the aggregate, you can see the, 00:20:03.150 --> 00:20:14.409 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: How compelling that is, if you're at the right stage of your career, and and you find benefit and value to the managed solutions that we provide. 00:20:14.600 --> 00:20:21.780 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Right? So, if… if you're… if there are check marks in both… in that and the, first of all, looking after the client. 00:20:21.780 --> 00:20:27.290 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Most effectively, if that box is checked using our solutions. 00:20:27.290 --> 00:20:42.949 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: then, of course, the compensation piece becomes very compelling, and for us, it's much more about the qualitative piece. So, in fact, a family business like yours is very appealing. 00:20:43.060 --> 00:21: