 Oops, I think you froze on me a little bit. 00:22:30.160 --> 00:22:31.500 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Well, have I lost you? 00:22:33.980 --> 00:22:37.189 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: I wonder if I've lost you, because I can't hear you now. 00:22:39.440 --> 00:22:45.710 [ADVISOR_1]: So, it has worked well. We are happy. We are not really… we are in it for enjoyment. 00:22:46.370 --> 00:22:57.069 [ADVISOR_1]: Every single day, we get up in the morning and say, what else we can do today for our clients, right? So, that is the enjoyment. I don't see that going away at all. 00:22:57.530 --> 00:22:58.020 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Yo. 00:22:58.020 --> 00:22:58.650 [ADVISOR_1]: And late. 00:22:59.220 --> 00:23:00.829 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: I… I agree with you. 00:23:00.870 --> 00:23:06.840 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: I completely agree with you. I think that you're… you've got a tremendous business, and 00:23:06.840 --> 00:23:24.059 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: you know, we've sort of… we've chosen a path that serves us and our advisors well, and you've chosen a unique path that does exactly the same thing. So I certainly, in con… in good conscience, wouldn't embarrass you or I by, you know, trying to influence that. I think that 00:23:24.130 --> 00:23:37.059 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: what you're doing makes perfect sense, and I think to give that up is philosophically counterintuitive for you, and it makes 100% sense, the way you're doing it. 00:23:37.060 --> 00:23:47.939 [ADVISOR_1]: Plus, when, you know, if we work with you, the thing is, you know, money does not mean anything. At this time, we are still… we are generating [REVENUE_AMOUNT] for the company, we still get [COMPENSATION_AMOUNT]. 00:23:47.940 --> 00:23:49.230 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Yeah, sure. 00:23:49.370 --> 00:23:52.280 [ADVISOR_1]: I mean… It is just a number. 00:23:52.280 --> 00:23:59.189 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Listen, most of the, most of the, advisory teams I work with, manage 00:23:59.320 --> 00:24:03.810 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: I'm gonna say anywhere from [BOOK_SIZE_AMOUNT] to [BOOK_SIZE_AMOUNT]