 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: It's just that we take, you know, we've got a back office staff of [BACK_OFFICE_TEAM_SIZE], I guess. 00:25:51.250 --> 00:25:57.780 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And we do everything through the CRM effectively, so we've created a point-and-click environment for our advisors. 00:25:57.780 --> 00:26:22.710 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And, straight through processing, everything maps to the CRM, so once data is added, it never has to be added again. And it all… all of the data is synchronized across, you know, for the financial planning, and it… everything is synchronized into the CRM. So, we create, really, a super efficient business for people, and then we give them performance that, and not that any of us would ever sell on 00:26:22.710 --> 00:26:28.949 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: performance at all, but on a risk-adjusted basis, it's very compelling. 00:26:29.140 --> 00:26:31.599 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: I don't know, just the… 00:26:32.080 --> 00:26:43.350 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: I'll sort of toot our own horn a little bit here, but our average sharp, let's say, is 120. You know, range is probably 105 to 130. 00:26:43.570 --> 00:26:58.279 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: downside captures, average about 45% across the portfolios, upside about 116%. So we can really do this on a tax-efficient, you know, risk-adjusted basis. We're providing returns from 00:26:58.340 --> 00:27:06.670 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: well, let's say net since inception, you know, we're probably 8.5 at the… at… 00:27:06.800 --> 00:27:22.550 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: the income portfolio, to, you know, 17, let's say, on the… on the growth, all growth side. So, yeah, so we… we feel like it's a very… it's… it's a very compelling platform, again, for the right 00:27:22.760 --> 00:27:25.840 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: The right business profile and the right advisor profile, right? 00:27:25.840 --> 00:27:32.719 [ADVISOR_1]: You are doing so well, and I'm really thankful to you for connecting on the. 00:27:32.720 --> 00:27:33.360 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Yeah. 00:27:33.360 --> 00:27:33.860 [ADVISOR_1]: Excellent. 00:27:33.860 --> 00:27:52.750 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: I, too. I'm glad that we identified, you know, you and your son as, to have a conversation with, because we never, we never know, and, listen, who knows, you know, whether our paths may cross down the road at some point, whether it's just on an industry level or, you know, running into each other, so… 00:27:52.750 --> 00:27:55.590 [ADVISOR_1]: It is a small, very small world. 00:27:55.590 --> 00:28:01.749 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Yes, of course. And we have, by the way, we have [OFFICE_FOOTPRINT], 00:28:01.860 --> 00:28:13.089 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: We have [HEAD_OFFICE_BUILDING_DESCRIPTION]. 00:28:13.090 --> 00:28:23.809 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And then, we have another building, a heritage building at [HEAD_OFFICE_ADDRESS], at [HEAD_OFFICE_INTERSECTION]. But then, we have [PM_TEAM_SIZE] client-facing portfolio managers at [OFFICE_BUILDING]. 00:28:23.810 --> 00:28:29.369 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: So… Which was our original, so who knows, you might be bumping into them once in a while, too. 00:28:30.360 --> 00:28:43.799 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Listen, I'll… we can leave it there. I wish you both, just a tremendous 2026 and continued success. If, for any reason I can ever be a resource, I would be delighted, and thank you. 00:28:43.800 --> 00:28:44.440 [ADVISOR_1]: event points. 00:28:44.440 --> 00:28:46.890 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Dora is always open to have a conversation. 00:28:46.890 --> 00:28:55.900 [ADVISOR_1]: Thank you very much, and definitely, if you are interested in attending our seminar on [SPECIALIZED_INVESTMENT_STRATEGY], you're more than welcome. We'll send you an invite. 00:28:55.900 --> 00:29:04.339 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Add me to… add me to your list. Okay. Okay, fellas, very good to chat with you. Okay, bye for now. 00:29:04.540 --> 00:29:05.609 [ADVISOR_1]: Happy birthday. 00:29:05.610 --> 00:29:06.430 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Okay.	completed	2026-05-22 02:14:03.05744+00	2026-05-22 02:14:31.815223+00	\N	\N
