ng the fact that, 00:07:16.210 --> 00:07:31.580 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: you know, I like to impart a question and say, you know, how are you paid, right? In that contract, are you earning a salary, right? And if the answer to that question is no, and it's purely commission-based, and I know who. 00:07:31.580 --> 00:07:33.450 [ADVISOR]: We can do what we want at the end of the day. 00:07:33.450 --> 00:07:54.479 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Right, absolutely, and I think that's just kind of an awareness, [ADVISOR], that most advisors within [CURRENT_DEALER] just kind of don't grasp, and it is a walled garden, I'll attest to that, right? And [CURRENT_DEALER] does a really good job of keeping their advisors within that walled garden. You know, they put a barbed wire fence all along the edge of it, so you can't even poke your head to see what's out there, right? 00:07:54.480 --> 00:07:56.230 [ADVISOR]: They do, but I have gloves to climb the fence. 00:07:56.230 --> 00:08:02.529 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Yeah, and a thick blanket to put it over. Hopefully, right? 00:08:02.530 --> 00:08:05.089 [ADVISOR]: So, I didn't want to interrupt, I just wanted to… 00:08:05.090 --> 00:08:24.659 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: No, no, no, that's fair, absolutely. I have a great understanding of what the conversation looks like, and [ADVISOR], I'm glad that we're here today kind of expanding on that notion, right? And again, just to mention that we are not, you know, a retail investment dealer, you know, offering the retail product shelf environment to the retail channel, right? 00:08:24.660 --> 00:08:35.440 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: We are an institutional money manager looking to, you know, exclusively partner with, you know, premium advisors in the industry, you know, who are ready to move beyond that kind of space, right? 00:08:35.610 --> 00:09:00.599 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And again, we're looking to work with, you know, those advisors who want to take their practice to the next level, okay? And I'll kind of just guide you through this presenta