ve for me, right? I can't help answer that. I can only give you the tools to be able to come up with that assessment. Ultimately, I'm gonna… 00:13:11.180 --> 00:13:32.599 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: We know what that competitive landscape is. You know, our compensation structure surely is reflective of one that is not only competitive, but industry leading in that sense. And we know this to be true. Like, we've… we've onboarded advisors coming from, you know, a myriad of financial institutions, if you will, right? 00:13:32.600 --> 00:13:34.969 [ADVISOR]: What… what do I do with my insurance book? 00:13:35.710 --> 00:13:42.290 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: So, that's a great question. So, your insurance book stays as is, right? that being said… 00:13:42.290 --> 00:13:43.850 [ADVISOR]: [CURRENT_DEALER] would can me. 00:13:44.350 --> 00:13:59.040 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Not necessarily. Not necessarily. So what we're saying is, you know, on that… so first and foremost, it's kind of two-pronged. Obviously, we wouldn't stay at [CURRENT_DEALER], if that's the answer to your question. So we have partnered with our MGA, which is [MGA]. 00:13:59.040 --> 00:14:08.420 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so, mo… most… all of that insurance book would be transferred to our partner, through our MGA [MGA], okay? 00:14:08.850 --> 00:14:12.999 [ADVISOR]: No. I don't own it. I don't own it. [CURRENT_DEALER] does. 00:14:13.770 --> 00:14:16.460 [ADVISOR]: That's why I asked if you were familiar with the structure. 00:14:16.460 --> 00:14:19.869 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: No, no, of course I am, but again, in terms of… 00:14:19.870 --> 00:14:25.240 [ADVISOR]: I can't move my insurance with me. They have to… Well… 00:14:26.330 --> 00:14:27.300 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: That's again. 00:14:27.300 --> 00:14:27.850 [ADVISOR]: It was a reason. 00:14:27.850 --> 00:14:28.500 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: One thing I challenge. 00:14:28.500 --> 00:14:29.540 [ADVISOR]: Actually, yeah… 00:14:29.690 --> 00:14:30.659 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: with the… 00:14:30.660 --> 00:14:34.689 [ADVISOR]: