lient relationships. 00:46:00.640 --> 00:46:01.700 [ADVISOR]: clients, yeah. 00:46:01.700 --> 00:46:12.429 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Yeah, new clients, expanding that client base, whatever that might be, or activities that you want to focus on outside of, you know, administrative tasks. Golf, exactly, right? 00:46:12.700 --> 00:46:37.199 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: And so, again, that's kind of our platform, and so what we've done, really with our technology platform, and kind of our promise to you, is really building out a platform that is a fully integrated ecosystem, where, again, all of our technologies connect and sync, seamlessly through our CRM platform, which is HubSpot. And again, with the goal of providing a very real and simplified way of essentially 00:46:37.200 --> 00:46:53.100 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: you know, operating your practice, right? And again, this is kind of a snapshot of some of the tools that we have operationally, that we provide advisors. It's at no cost to you. And again, you said, you know, [OPTIMIZE_REP], listen, you know, I don't pay anything. Realization… 00:46:53.100 --> 00:46:53.670 [ADVISOR]: That's a lot. 00:46:53.670 --> 00:46:54.660 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: advisors do. 00:46:54.660 --> 00:46:56.490 [ADVISOR]: I, I, I pay for… 00:46:57.000 --> 00:47:04.949 [ADVISOR]: Yeah, so I don't pay any dealer fees, per se, but I have to pay, some technology. 00:47:05.200 --> 00:47:13.710 [ADVISOR]: Right, and through my laptop, and then I have Salesforce, and OnePlan, and hearsay, and all that stuff. 00:47:13.710 --> 00:47:21.810 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Yeah, yeah, yeah, and again, this, it varies, but on average, it's anywhere from [MONTHLY_COST_RANGE] a month, on average, in the industry, right? 00:47:21.810 --> 00:47:30.670 [ADVISOR]: Yep, and I have to pay for it for my… I just hired my old manager, actually, I have to pay for it for him, and then my staff member, I have to pay for it for her. 00:47:30.670 --> 00:47:35.140 [OPTIMIZE_REP]: Right, so now, you know, times 3, right, i